---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
	<div class="text-center mb-12">
		<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4">
			Hello, Astronaut!
		</h1>
		<p class="text-xl text-base-content/80">
			Welcome to the official <a href="https://astro.build/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Astro</a> blog starter template.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
		<div class="card-body">
			<p class="text-lg">
				This template serves as a lightweight, minimally-styled starting point for anyone looking to build a personal
				website, blog, or portfolio with Astro.
			</p>
			<p class="text-lg">
				This template comes with a few integrations already configured in your
				<code class="bg-base-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">astro.config.mjs</code> file. You can customize your setup with
				<a href="https://astro.build/integrations" class="text-primary hover:underline">Astro Integrations</a> to add tools like Tailwind,
				React, or Vue to your project.
			</p>
			<p class="text-lg">Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the template:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg ml-4">
				<li>Edit this page in <code class="bg-base-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
				<li>Edit the site header items in <code class="bg-base-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/components/Header.astro</code></li>
				<li>Add your name to the footer in <code class="bg-base-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/components/Footer.astro</code></li>
				<li>Check out the included blog posts in <code class="bg-base-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/content/blog/</code></li>
				<li>Customize the blog post page layout in <code class="bg-base-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></li>
			</ul>
			<p class="text-lg mt-4">
				Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to
				<a href="https://docs.astro.build/" class="text-primary hover:underline">read the docs</a>
				or <a href="https://astro.build/chat" class="text-primary hover:underline">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
